- First Fit: Place the item in the first bin that can accommodate it.
- Best Fit: Place the item in the bin where it fits best, minimizing the remaining space.
- Worst Fit: Place the item in the bin that leaves the worst (most fragmented) remaining space.
- Random Fit: Place the item randomly in any bin that can accommodate it.
- Others: Any other heuristic strategies.

