### Approach
The approach involves creating unique mathematical expressions using a combination of allowed operations such as mathematical functions, array operations, and control flow structures. Each function will use different numpy functions and mathematical operations to compute the priority score. The goal is to ensure each implementation is unique and efficient, avoiding any explicit loops that would lead to high time complexity.

